2001-06-10  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Moved the transformation code to Point class

	* Changed the internal coordinate system to follow the usual
	  mathematical coordinate system rather than screen coordinates

2001-05-29  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Store vertices as Point objects instead of storing them as two
	  separate fixed point values (cleanup, no functional changes)

2001-05-28  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Prepared documentation for the 0.2 release

	* Undo support for polylines and rectangles

	* Extended polyline tool to make it possible to connect separate
	  polylines to create one combined polyline

2001-05-26  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Undo support for delete, edit, ellipses and labels

	* Confirm operations which would discard changes made to the
	  current figure

	* Added generic framework level support for undoing operations

	* Splitted FileIcon.cxx of ESP Widget Set to avoid always linking
	  icon loading code (not needed for VRFig)

2001-05-25  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Added framework for textual elements and a text label which
	  implements the interface. Also a new tool for creating and
	  editing the labels (and other textual elements).

2001-05-24  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Bug fix: Bogus XML parser error due to incorrect buffer
	  allocation when loading files longer than 1024 bytes

	* Increased the maximum select distance used by the tools

2001-05-23  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Cleaned up the code and user interface for the initial beta
	  release

	* Added the about dialog and deactivated those buttons which are
	  not yet fully implemented

	* Added new element: Ellipse (and the drawing tool for it)

2001-05-22  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Added new element: Rectangle (and the drawing tool for it)

	* Added new interface and tool: Elements implementing the
	  Controllable interface can be edited by moving control points
	  (using the EditTool)

	* Added new tool: Delete

	* Added new tool: Move

2001-05-21  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Implemented the deserialization framework using the Expat XML
	  parsing library. Polyline based figures can now be loaded and
	  saved, yahoo :)

2001-05-20  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Modified the FileChooser from the ESP Widget Set to use flpda
	  and match Agenda VR3 look and feel

2001-05-19  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* The first element implements the full element framework:
	  Polyline

	* Generic framework for elements and tools

2001-05-18  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Added new generic tool selection widget

2001-05-16  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Commented away the experimental user interface code which tries
	  to guess what the user is drawing (concentrate on making the
	  basic things work first)

	* Extended FLTK with few functions to draw in xorred mode

2001-05-08  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Fixed point arithmetic for solving the required geometric
	  calculations without floating point instructions

2001-05-05  Johannes Lehtinen  <johannes.lehtinen@iki.fi>

	* Project started, imported the initial files to the CVS
	  repository
